HEADWORD: Shredless
<hw>Shred"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having no shreds; without a
shred.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>And those which waved are <qex>shredless</qex> dust ere now.</q>
<rj><qau>Byron.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

